  <num>15-711</num>
  <heading>Deposit or security for costs in Superior Court.</heading>
  <text>Nonresidents of the District of Columbia may commence suits in the Superior Court of the District of Columbia without first giving security for costs, but upon motion may be required to give security pursuant to section 15-703  .</text>
